OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780563951
OL,3,C11 police officers injured in
OL,4,CSouthampton during violent protests
OL,6,F11 police officers and a police dog
OL,7,Fhave been injured during protests held
OL,8,Fin Southampton overnight.
OL,10,FHundreds gathered in the Portswood
OL,11,Farea on Tuesday evening, following the
OL,12,Frelease of bodycam footage of the
OL,13,Farrest of Henry Nowak.
OL,15,FThe unrest came amid an outcry about
OL,16,Fthe policing response to the murder
OL,17,Fafter the university student's killer
OL,18,Fclaimed he had been the victim of a
OL,19,Fracial attack while Mr Nowak was
OL,20,Fhandcuffed by police as he lay dying.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
