PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780563951
OL,3,C11 police officers injured in
OL,4,CSouthampton during violent protests
OL,6,FTwo people have so far been arrested
OL,7,Ffor their part in the protest, but
OL,8,FHampshire Police confirmed that number
OL,9,Fwill rise.
OL,11,FChief Constable Alexis Boon said: "We
OL,12,Funderstand and appreciate as police
OL,13,Fofficers that we are accountable for
OL,14,Four actions. What we ask, however, is
OL,15,Fthat those actions are judged through
OL,16,Ffair and transparent processes. In
OL,17,Fthis case, that process is already
OL,18,Funderway with the IOPC conducting
OL,19,Ftheir independent investigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780563951
OL,3,C11 police officers injured in
OL,4,CSouthampton during violent protests
OL,6,F"What we, as a society, cannot accept
OL,7,Fis the violent scenes we saw in
OL,8,FSouthampton last night.
OL,10,F"Some clearly arrived intent on
OL,11,Fcausing disorder and trouble. We saw
OL,12,Fbottles thrown, makeshift weapons
OL,13,Fused, damage caused to the homes and
OL,14,Fvehicles of innocent residents and
OL,15,Fthreats and violence directed towards
OL,16,Four officers.
OL,18,F"As a result, 11 officers and one
OL,19,Fpolice dog were injured, while trying
OL,20,Fto do their job to protect the
OL,21,Fcommunities that we serve.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780563951
OL,3,C11 police officers injured in
OL,4,CSouthampton during violent protests
OL,6,F"While we are forced to deal with
OL,7,Fthose determined to spark fear and
OL,8,Fdivision, our finite resources are
OL,9,Ftaken away from those who need it most.
OL,11,F"I know how intimidating the scenes
OL,12,Ffrom last night must have been for
OL,13,Fthose living and working in the area
OL,14,Fand to you, I must stress, we have
OL,15,Fincredibly experienced teams of
OL,16,Fofficers who are working around the
OL,17,Fclock to keep you safe - that is our
OL,18,Fabsolute priority.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780563951
OL,3,C11 police officers injured in
OL,4,CSouthampton during violent protests
OL,6,F"You will see more of my officers
OL,7,Fpatrolling your neighbourhoods over
OL,8,Fthe coming days and specialist
OL,9,Fintelligence teams are supporting
OL,10,Fthose on the frontline.
OL,12,F"My officers bravely and robustly
OL,13,Ffaced violence with professionalism
OL,14,Fand courage last night and this
OL,15,Fmorning our investigation is underway
OL,16,Fto identify those responsible for the
OL,17,Fdisorder.
OL,19,F"Last night, we made two arrests and
OL,20,Fthat number will rise as those
OL,21,Finvestigations continue.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780563951
OL,3,C11 police officers injured in
OL,4,CSouthampton during violent protests
OL,6,F"I know that since the release of the
OL,7,Fbody-worn video footage from the night
OL,8,Fof Henry Nowak's murder, there is a
OL,9,Fdesire for answers and accountability
OL,10,Fbut that must be done in the right way
OL,11,Fand not used as an excuse to threaten
OL,12,Fand intimidate my officers and bring
OL,13,Fviolence to our streets causing fear
OL,14,Fand harm to those living and working
OL,15,Fin Hampshire and the Isle of Wight."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
